results.deck: Elite is a developer and publisher of computer games and mobile games active since 1984
results.description: Â Elite was founded as Richard Wilcox Software and became Elite in 1984 and went on to release games primarily for the C64 and Spectrum ZX. After 25 years of existence, Elite now focusses on developing games for mobile phones, some original games and mostly ports of classic computer games
